<H3> <TI>   Shandong QINGDAO COMMERCIAL PAPER Starts Publication </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1103111094 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 9 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1103111094 </F>
<F P=104>  Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] With the approval of the propaganda department of 
the provincial party committee and of the provincial press and 
publication bureau, QINGDAO SHANGBAO [QINGDAO COMMERCIAL PAPER] 
recently formally started publication. This is a comprehensive 
economic paper run by the financial and trade office under the 
Qingdao city government. This paper will energetically 
propagate the principles, policies, and pertinent rules and 
regulations concerning economic work of the party and the state, 
positively explore the law of the development of market economy 
and the theory of market economic management, and reflect the 
demands and voice of consumers. 

</TEXT>

