<H3> <TI>   Vice Premier Li Lanqing Meets UN Officials </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1803090294 Beijing XINHUA in English 0836 GMT 18 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1803090294 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 18 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Vice-Premier 
Li Lanqing met with Jean Gurunlian, executive secretary of World 
Symposium on Trade Efficiency of the United Nations, and his 
party here today. 
  The visitors arrived here Wednesday [16 March] as guests of 
the Chinese Ministry of Foreign Trade and Economic Cooperation. 
  The U.N. symposium is scheduled to be held from October 17 
to 
21 in the United States. 

</TEXT>

