<F P=100> North Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Tianjin Secretary at Ceremony for Start of New Term </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK0203122894 Tianjin People's Radio in Mandarin 1000 GMT 1 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK0203122894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tianjin People's Radio </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The party school of the Tianjin Municipal CPC 
Committee held a ceremony for the beginning of the 1994 spring 
semester on the morning of 1 March. 
  Gao Dezhan, secretary of the municipal party committee and 
president of the party school, attended and addressed the 
ceremony. Fang Fengyou and Zheng Zhiying, standing committee 
members of the municipal party committee, attended the ceremony. 
  Gao Dezhan pointed out in his speech: The municipal party 
committee has attached extreme importance to the cadres' 
training and study work. The party committees at various levels 
across the municipality have paid high attention to the study of 
the Third Volume of the "Selected Works of Deng Xiaoping." The 
broad masses of cadres are enthusiastically engaged in the 
study. An upsurge of studying theories has started in the 
municipality and a gratifying situation has emerged. 
  Gao Dezhan stressed: We should firmly grasp the fundamental 
principle of linking theory with practice, pay attention to the 
results of study, and promote the study work. Linking theory 
with practice is a fine style of study that our party has 
consistently encouraged. In the course of study, we should 
proceed from the actual conditions of Tianjin, keep close 
contact with reality, use the vivid facts that the people have 
personally experienced to deepen the (?understanding) about the 
party's basic theories and basic line, and strengthen the 
awareness of firm implementation. The most important factor for 
studying Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory is to master the ability 
in consciously applying this powerful ideological weapon to 
solve the realistic problems cropping up in the course of 
reform, opening up, and modernization; and to upgrade our 
ideology, understanding, and leadership ability. Only by so 
doing will we able to [words indistinct] and to make real 
results. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

