<F P=100> North Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Beijing Secretary Attends Organizational Work Conference </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK0403042994 Beijing BEIJING RIBAO in Chinese 19 Feb 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> SK0403042994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing BEIJING RIBAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By Yan Liqiang (0917 0500 1730): "Exert Strenuous Efforts </F>
to Firmly Grasp the Party's Ideological and Theoretical 
Construction and the Building of Leading Bodies To Guarantee a 
Long Period of Peace and Security in China"] 
  [Excerpts] The municipal organizational work conference 
was held yesterday. Chen Xitong, secretary of the municipal 
party committee, stressed in his speech: We must uphold the 
party's leadership and strengthen party building in the course 
of accelerating reform and development. In this year's 
organizational work, the task of prime importance is to 
continuously exert strenuous efforts to firmly grasp the party's 
ideological and theoretical construction and the building of 
leading bodies and to guarantee the implementation of the 
central authorities' major reform policy decisions and the 
capital's stability and unity. 
  First of all, Chen Xitong fully affirmed the prominent 
achievements in Tianjin's organizational work, and at the same 
time, he pointed out: This is a crucial year for 
comprehensively implementing the guidelines of the third plenary 
session of the 14th CPC Central Committee. Making all-out 
efforts to safeguard the capital's political and social 
stability and guaranteeing the smooth implementation of the 
central authorities' major reform policy decisions is a major 
matter of prime importance in the work of Beijing Municipality 
and in organizational work. The organizational work should 
serve this overall situation, and strenuous efforts should be 
made to grasp two basic construction. First, we should pay 
attention to ideological and theoretical construction, 
strengthen study of Marxism, Mao Zedong Thought, and Deng 
Xiaoping's theory on building socialism with Chinese 
characteristics, strive to raise the ideological and theoretical 
level of party-member cadres, formulate plans, and provide 
evaluations. Second, we should pay attention to the building of 
leading bodies, and after selecting a number of outstanding 
young cadres as the new leading bodies during the district and 
county end-of-term elections, be determined to select a number 
of outstanding young cadres for the leading bodies of the 
municipal party committee and of various departments, 
committees, offices, and bureaus of the municipal government, 
and install the echelon well. Meanwhile, it is necessary to 
strengthen the building of grass-roots party organizations, with 
an emphasis in consolidating the backward party branches and 
strengthening the building of party branches in three types of 
foreign-funded enterprises, people-run enterprises, high-tech 
enterprises, and various new economic organizations. Chen 
Xitong stressed: Strengthening party building is a fundamental 
task in consolidating the party's leadership and guaranteeing a 
long period of peace and stability in the country and we must 
grasp it firmly and successfully. 
  Chen Guangwen, deputy secretary of the municipal party 
committee, delivered a report at the conference. He summarized 
last year's work and put forth this year's tasks. 
  In 1993, in carrying out the municipal organizational work, 
we persisted in emancipating the mind, seeking truth from facts, 
conscientiously implementing all tasks set forth by the 14th 
party congress and the seventh municipal party congress, 
realized the municipal party committee's demand of 
comprehensively overpassing the work of last year, and achieved 
a series of breakthroughs. 
  Leading cadres enhanced awareness in the study of the theory 
on building socialism with Chinese characteristics and achieved 
noticeable results in this aspect; the selection of young cadres 
was strengthened and the structure of leading bodies greatly 
improved; the contingent of reserve cadres was expanded and 
their management strengthened; and the exchange of cadres 
increased, the channels rose in number, and the scope expanded. 
We summarized a number of typical examples in building the 
grass-roots party organizations and consolidated a batch of 
backward party branches; selected "10 outstanding" communist 
party members and cultivated an image of communist party members 
of the new period; and began to conduct organizational reform in 
party and government organs, and achieved progress in 
experimenting with the public service system. 
  The ideas for the municipal organizational work in 1994 are 
to take Deng Xiaoping's theory on building socialism with 
Chinese characteristics and the party's basic line as the 
guidance, further emancipate the mind, act in connection with 
the party's central task, strengthen and improve party building, 
strive to make new breakthroughs in strengthening the building 
of leading bodies and grass-roots party organizations and 
expanding strength in reform of the cadre personnel system, and 
provide an organizational guarantee for acccelerating the 
development of the socialist market economy, fulfilling all 
reform and construction tasks of this year, and realizing the 
objective of becoming well-off three years ahead of schedule. 
[passage omitted] 
  Wang Tong, Ouyang Wenan, Yang Chaoshi, and Qiang Wei, member 
of the standing committee of the municipal party committee, and 
Li Yongan, secretary of the municipal Discipline Inspection 
Commission, attended the conference. 

</TEXT>

